title: Sydney Tower
author: JJStrbik
pages:
Sydney Tower or
Centrepoint Tower
is the tallest
man-made structure in
the city of Sydney,
and is the second
tallest observation
tower in the Southern
Hemisphere. Standing
at a total of 309
metres, the tower is a
prominent tourist
attraction within
Sydney.

Created by: JJStrbik

wrong location
because of space.

and this thing is
terrifying.
